<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - BA.KonnexResources</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <!--begin::Web font -->

    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.js"></script>
    <!--Bootstrap5 -->

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.13.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!--end::Base Styles -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" media="screen" runat="server" />
</head>

<body>
    <header class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-light pr">
        <div class="container custom-container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" asp-page="/Index">
                <img class="img-fluid w-100" src="/images/konnex-logo.png" />
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapsibleNavbar">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="collapsibleNavbar">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <div class="dropdown">
                            <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" role="button" id="dropdownMenuLink"
                                data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
                                About
                            </a>

                            <ul class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenuLink">
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/KonnexResources">Konnex Resources</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Phoenix Copper Limited</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link " asp-page="/ESG">ESG</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <div class="dropdown">
                            <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" role="button" id="dropdownMenuLink"
                                data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
                                Empire Mine
                            </a>

                            <ul class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenuLink">
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-page="/Project">The Project</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="~/Project/project/#faq">FAQ</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">History</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/career">News</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link href=" #" role="button" id="dropdownMenuLink" data-bs-toggle="dropdown"
                            aria-expanded="false">
                            Management
                        </a>
                    </li>

                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#">Contact</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="container-fluid p-0">
        <main role="main" class="pb-3">
            @RenderBody()
        </main>
    </div>

    <footer class="container-fluid">
        <div class="container py-5">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 col-6 social-icons">
                    <h3 class="text-uppercase mb-0">Follow Us</h3>
                    <div class="">
                        <!-- Twitter -->
                        <a href="#" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                        <!-- Linkedin -->
                        <a href="#" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i></a>
                        <!-- Facebook -->
                        <a href="#" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                        <!-- Instagram -->
                        <a href="#" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-6">
                    <ul class="privacy-links">
                        <li><a href="#">Terms</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Privacy</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Sitemap</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/multislider.js"></script>
    <script>
        $('#basicSlider').multislider({
            continuous: true,
            duration: 2000
        });
        $('#mixedSlider').multislider({
            duration: 750,
            interval: 3000
        });
    </script>
    <script>
        AOS.init();
    </script>
    @await RenderSectionAsync("Scripts", required: false)

    <div class="modal fade modal-bg" id="wildlife-card" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel"
        aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content wildlife-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Wildlife & Vegetation</h5>
                    @* <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button> *@
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>Konnex Resources hired an independent environmental engineering company to collect extensive
                        environmental data over three years. The data collected concludes the Company’s activities at
                        the Empire Mine will not be damaging to local wildlife or plant life and will not affect the
                        biodiversity of the area.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal fade modal-bg" id="water-card" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel"
        aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content water-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Water</h5>
                    @* <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button> *@
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>The mines are dry and situated 900 feet above the water table. All water will evaporate or be
                        absorbed into the ground. Despite this, the Company has 12 groundwater monitoring wells to
                        establish baseline water composition prior to mine production and will continue monitoring the
                        wells during the life of the mine.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal fade modal-bg" id="electricity-card" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel"
        aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content electricity-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Electricity</h5>
                    @* <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button> *@
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>There is already power access on the mountain which comes from Idaho’s remarkable renewable
                        energy grid. Idaho has the 3rd highest percentage of electricity generated from renewables in
                        the United States at 76%. The Company is looking at more ways to reduce its carbon footprint and
                        utilize the state’s clean energy.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal fade modal-bg" id="noise-card" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel"
        aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content noise-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Noise, Ligh and Dust Pollution</h5>
                    @* <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button> *@
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>Noise, light and dust pollution are all items that will be addressed in detail in the
                        Environmental Impact Statement. Konnex will be required to prove the project does not create
                        noise, light and dust pollution to begin and remain in operation. The project is not permitted
                        to exceed a 10-decibel noise threshold beyond one mile of the mine site. For context, the sound
                        of regular breathing is about 10 decibels. The Company will also be required to fit diffusers on
                        the headlamps of trucks and provide ways for abating dust.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
